              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Forward-emitted charged particles",
                "were detected in the high resolution array located",
                "80-cm downstream of the target and covered scattering",
                "angles from 2.1 deg to 12.4 deg. The array contained",
                "14 dE-E telescopes each consisting of a 1.5 mm thick",
                "double-sided Si strip dE detector followed by a 4-cm-",
                "thick CsI(Tl) E detector. The dE detectors are 6.4 cm",
                "x 6.4 cm in area, with each face divided into 32",
                "strips. Each E detector consisted of four separate",
                "CsI(Tl) elements, each spanning a quadrant of the",
                "preceding Si detector."
              ]
            }
          ],
